name: Dark Ivysaur - 6
extCardText:
Poké-BODY — Vine Pull
One during your turn when Dark Ivysaur retreats, choose 1 of your opponent's Benched Pokémon and switch it with his or her Active Pokémon.
extAttack1:
[GG] Fury Strikes
Your opponent puts 3 markers onto his or her Pokémon (divided as he or she chooses). (More than 1 marker can be put on the same Pokémon.) Then, this attack does 10 damage to each Pokémon for each marker on it. Don't apply Weakness and Resistance. Remove the markers at the end of the turn.

name: Dark Venusaur - 7
extAttack1:
[GGG] Horrid Pollen (30)
Flip 2 coins. If 1 is heads, the Defending Pokémon is now Asleep and Poisoned. If both are heads, the Defending Pokémon is now Confused and Poisoned. If both are tails, the Defending Pokémon is now Paralyzed and Poisoned.

name: Electabuzz - 1
extAttack1:
[L] Thundershock (10)
Flip a coin. If heads, defender is now Paralyzed.
extAttack2:
[1L] Thunderpunch (30+)
Flip a coin. If heads, this attack does 30 damage plus 10 more damage. If tails, this attack does 30 damage and Electabuzz does 10 damage to itself.

name: Professor Elm - 3
extCardText: Shuffle your hand into your deck. Then, draw 7 cards. You can't play any more Trainer cards this turn.

name: Rocket's Scizor - 4
